channel.title: Help, my Rs2.io on 508 dont work
channel.description:
Hello, I've just started on 508's And my Rs2.io compiler doesnt seem to work the code writed in it, looks like this
[code]@echo off cd ../src "C:\Program\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin/javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/io/rs2/*.java pause [/code]
In my classpath there is:
[code]CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin;%CLASSPATH%; [/code] And i tried with the Rs2.io with this
[code]C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin/javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/io/rs2/*.java pause [/code] If you can help me, please reply or tell me the code ~ Yóur Mastér

item.title: Help, my Rs2.io on 508 dont work
item.dc:creator: @kickingjamie kickingjamie
item.description:
@kickingjamie wrote:

you need to set it to work with your jdk version , so jdk1.6.0_11 would turn into your jdk version.
